  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exovoid Carnage</strong> is an intense <strong>WAVE-BASED ARENA SHOOTER</strong> that cranks up the chaos to eleven! <strong>SHOOT! SHRED! SURVIVE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/65eee0312010a6aafefbb1b8735320b3.poster.avif?t=1728060478\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/65eee0312010a6aafefbb1b8735320b3.webm?t=1728060478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/65eee0312010a6aafefbb1b8735320b3.mp4?t=1728060478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re dropped onto the colossal Leviathan Station, an alien fortress the size of a planet. Armed with only a gun and no time to lose, you’re launched into a relentless fight for survival. Battle through <u>waves</u> of vicious aliens, blast your way to victory, and get catapulted to the next room!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/423b04fe059f18f9d9bb69b632421b7a.avif?t=1728060478\" width=720 height=384 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip game-changing power-ups like <strong>Rapid Fire</strong>, <strong>Double Damage</strong>, and the devastating <strong>Saw-blade Tornado</strong>.  As you progress, the enemies get fiercer, but so do you. Every death means a new chance to try again with advantages based on your previous run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/c7ed8fe50c77078554f877272f74fdc4.avif?t=1728060478\" width=800 height=426 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far can you go? Sharpen your skills, beat your high score, and see if you have what it takes to survive EXOVOID CARNAGE!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exovoid Carnage</strong> is an intense <strong>WAVE-BASED ARENA SHOOTER</strong> that cranks up the chaos to eleven! <strong>SHOOT! SHRED! SURVIVE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/65eee0312010a6aafefbb1b8735320b3.poster.avif?t=1728060478\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/65eee0312010a6aafefbb1b8735320b3.webm?t=1728060478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/65eee0312010a6aafefbb1b8735320b3.mp4?t=1728060478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re dropped onto the colossal Leviathan Station, an alien fortress the size of a planet. Armed with only a gun and no time to lose, you’re launched into a relentless fight for survival. Battle through <u>waves</u> of vicious aliens, blast your way to victory, and get catapulted to the next room!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102800/extras/423b04fe059f18f9d9bb69b632421b7a.avif?t=1728060478\" width=720 height=384 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip game-changing power-ups like <strong>Rapid Fire</strong>, <strong>Double Damage</strong>, and the devastating <strong>Saw-blade Tornado</strong>.  As you progress, the enemies get fiercer, but so do you. Every death means a new chance to try again with advantages based on your previous run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a